title: Urusei Yatsura - Lum the invader girl Complete TV series
description:
Urusei Yatsura (AKA Lum, the invader girl)


Complete series, episodes 1-195. 
Japanese audio with english subtitles. 
Mkv files.
Quality is what you would expect from a 20 year old anime.

I cant get media player to play the subs, but VLC Media Player works fine.


This is an oldie, but very, very good. Its also out of print, so it&#039;s neraly impossible to find all original volumes.And it was never released as R2 dvd. So, thanks to donkey brain publishers, it&#039;s up to us to keep this one alive (I would really like to purchase the originals, but I can&#039;t find them anywhere and thanks to not so "free trade" I cant watch legally purchased R1 dvds on my R2 player - or can I?;))

For those who don&#039;t know the series its about an alien girl who comes to earth in order to repossess the planet. It&#039;s up to a very unlucky and lustful highschooler named Ataru to save the world by defeating Lum in combat. He ends up (accidentally) proposing to her. Its hilarious.
